  [2]: https://docs.oracle.com/en/java/javase/17/docs/api/java.base/java/lang/ProcessBuilder.html
  [3]: https://docs.oracle.com/en/java/javase/17/docs/api/java.desktop/java/awt/Desktop.html
  [4]: https://docs.oracle.com/javase/tutorial/uiswing/concurrency/dispatch.html

